Name   : AVtools release 03
Author : Dominique B‚r‚ziat
Date   : May 02
Email  : Dominique.Bereziat@inria.fr

This package provides some commands and scripts to support 
AV-protocol in the Mupfel shell. It can be easily adapted 
for other shell as (c)sh.

Just copy bin, scripts and man folders in your usr hierarchy.
For feedback, send a mail to Dominique.Bereziat@inria.fr

R01 : first public release.
R02 : adding "apterm" and "stghelp" scripts, improving "open" script.
R03 : adding "edit" script, improving "avserver" script,
 	  applfind and applwrit accept now a full application name (not
 	  necessary AES-formatted).

